import { Box, Card, CardActionArea, CardMedia,CardContent, Typography } from '@mui/material'
import imgRebajas from '../../img/desktop-rebajas.webp'

const SectionCategory = ({ responsive }) => {
    return (
        <Box>
            <Card sx={{background:'inherit', padding: '24px'}}>
                <CardActionArea>
                    <CardContent sx={{ display:'flex', flexDirection:'column',justifyContent:'center', alignItem:'center'}}>
                        <Typography gutterBottom variant="h5" component="div" >
                            Lizard
                        </Typography>
                        <Typography variant="body2" color="text.secondary">
                            Lizards are a widespread group of squamate reptiles, with over 6,000
                            species, ranging across all continents except Antarctica
                        </Typography>
                    </CardContent>
                    <CardMedia
                        component="img"
                        height="140"
                        image={imgRebajas}
                        alt="rebajas"
                        sx={{height: '100%',
                        objectFit: 'cover'}}
                    />
                </CardActionArea>
            </Card>
        </Box>
    )
}

export default SectionCategory
